---
title: Slow-Cooked Chicken & Creamy Bacon Risoni Bake with Broccoli & Parmesan Cheese
description: Patience is going to be key with this dish. We understand how tempting it is to dig in as soon as possible - it smells so good - but you’ll be glad for those extra minutes. Allowing the succulent chicken to marinate in the creamy stew will add a burst of flavour to every bite.

*Unfortunately, this
week’s baby broccoli was
in short supply, so we’ve
replaced it with broccoli.
Don’t worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
